(23, 'com_content.article', 'No bill for Delhi consumers using up to 200 units electricity: Arvind Kejriwal', 'no-bill-for-delhi-consumers-using-up-to-200-units-electricity-arvind-kejriwal', '<h1><span style=\"font-size: 18pt;\"><strong>No bill for Delhi consumers using up to 200 units electricity: Arvind </strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 18pt;\"><strong>Kejriwal</strong></span></h1>\r\n<p><span class=\"m-story-header__intro\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">\"Delhi Electricity Bill New Rates: Arvind Kejriwal said, \"Since independence, VIPs - politicians and officers have been provided free electricity and water from taxpayers\' money. Now the aam aadmi will also get basic services free, as a matter of right.\"</span></span></p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p><span class=\"m-story-header__intro\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><strong><img src=\"image/arvind-kejriwal.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"759\" height=\"422\" /></strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Residents of Delhi consuming up to 200 units of power will no longer have to pay any electricity bill. Making the announcement, Delhi Chief Minister Arvind Kejriwal said, “Since independence, VIPs – politicians and officers have been provided free electricity and water from taxpayers’ money.</span></p>\r\n', 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1, '{\"article_layout\":\"\",\"show_title\":\"\",\"link_titles\":\"\",\"show_tags\":\"\",\"show_intro\":\"\",\"info_block_position\":\"\",\"info_block_show_title\":\"\",\"show_category\":\"\",\"link_category\":\"\",\"show_parent_category\":\"\",\"link_parent_category\":\"\",\"show_associations\":\"\",\"show_author\":\"\",\"link_author\":\"\",\"show_create_date\":\"\",\"show_modify_date\":\"\",\"show_publish_date\":\"\",\"show_item_navigation\":\"\",\"show_icons\":\"\",\"show_print_icon\":\"\",\"show_email_icon\":\"\",\"show_vote\":\"\",\"show_hits\":\"\",\"show_noauth\":\"\",\"urls_position\":\"\",\"alternative_readmore\":\"\",\"article_page_title\":\"\",\"show