(54, 22, 1, '', '2019-08-01 10:52:16', 827, 2917, 'd29658cd87d6a06a7b0576b7b05de391698628cb', '{\"id\":22,\"asset_id\":84,\"title\":\"In pictures: Nipah\\u2019s deadly grip on Kozhikode\",\"alias\":\"in-pictures-nipah-s-deadly-grip-on-kozhikode\",\"introtext\":\"<h1 class=\\\"title\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 14pt;\\\"><strong>In pictures: Nipah\\u2019s deadly grip on Kozhikode<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/h1>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size: 14pt;\\\"><strong><iframe src=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/embed\\/KteREaFAPNE\\\" width=\\\"724\\\" height=\\\"579\\\" frameborder=\\\"0\\\" allowfullscreen=\\\"allowfullscreen\\\"><\\/iframe><\\/strong><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\">On May 22, the\\u00a0death<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.thehindu.com\\/tag\\/1167-1165-1151\\/death\\/?utm=bodytag\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\"><strong>\\u00a0<\\/strong><\\/a>toll due to the Nipah virus outbreak touched 11. Laboratory tests have confirmed the presence of the virus in blood and fluid samples taken from all the victims in Kozhikode.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt;\\\">A team from the All India Institute of Medical Sciences (AIIMS) and National Centre for Disease Control (NCDC) has arrived to assist the State\\u00a0Health\\u00a0Department. The State government is also considering seeking the help of the World Health Organisation.<\\/span><\\/p>\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":1,\"catid\":\"10\",\"created\":\"2019-08-01 10:52:16\",\"created_by\":\"827\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2019-08-01 10:52:16\",\"modified_by\":null,\"checked_out\":null,\"checked_out_time\":null,\"publish_up\":\"2019-08-01 10:52:16\",\"publish_down\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\",\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"